     Basic Editing

Ctrl + Space → Content Assist (auto code completion)

Ctrl + / → Toggle comment/uncomment for a single line

Ctrl + Shift + / → Add block comment

Ctrl + Shift + \ → Remove block comment

Ctrl + D → Delete the current line

Ctrl + Shift + F → Format code

Ctrl + Alt + ↓ / ↑ → Duplicate line

Alt + ↑ / ↓ → Move line

🔹 Navigation & Search

Ctrl + Shift + R → Open Resource (search any file in workspace)

Ctrl + Shift + T → Open Type (search any class/interface)

Ctrl + Shift + G → Find references in workspace

Ctrl + O → Show Outline (methods/fields of class)

Ctrl + E → Switch between open editors

F3 → Open declaration (go to definition of class/method/variable)

Alt + ← / → → Go backward/forward in navigation history

🔹 Code Generation & Refactoring

Alt + Shift + R → Rename variable/method/class

Alt + Shift + M → Extract method

Alt + Shift + L → Extract local variable

Alt + Shift + I → Inline variable/method

Alt + Shift + Z → Surround with try/catch or other templates

Alt + Shift + T → Refactor menu (quick access to all refactorings)

Ctrl + Shift + O → Organize imports

Alt + Shift + S → Generate code (getters/setters/constructors/toString)

🔹 Running & Debugging

Ctrl + F11 → Run last launched

F11 → Debug last launched

F5 → Step into

F6 → Step over

F7 → Step return

Ctrl + Shift + B → Toggle breakpoint

Ctrl + Shift + F11 → Run selected test case with JUnit/TestNG

🔹 Editing & Productivity

Ctrl + Shift + L → Show all shortcut keys

Ctrl + Shift + P → Jump to matching bracket

Ctrl + 1 → Quick fix (auto-suggest fixes, imports, corrections)

Ctrl + Shift + C → Comment/uncomment block

Ctrl + Alt + H → Open call hierarchy (who is calling this method)

Ctrl + Shift + M → Add missing import for selected class

🔹 Views & Workspace

Alt + Shift + Q, C → Open Console view

Alt + Shift + Q, P → Open Package Explorer

Alt + Shift + Q, H → Open Hierarchy view

Ctrl + Shift + F4 → Close all open editors

Ctrl + M → Maximize/minimize editor
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     
     